Let's pray together.

00:36:33.489 --> 00:36:39.539
God, thank you so much just for what an unexpected gift and joy it is for me to be here in Milford today.

00:36:39.579 --> 00:36:47.731
I thank you, Lord, for so many people that are here and seeking and hungry to know more about you, to raise their family, to love and follow you.

00:36:47.771 --> 00:36:54.401
And I think one of the great lies of the enemy that I want to pray against right now is that we're not called or we're not important.

00:36:54.562 --> 00:36:57.426
Our role doesn't really have value.

00:36:57.666 --> 00:36:59.729
May that lie be dispelled.

00:37:00.029 --> 00:37:03.033
May that voice of the enemy be quieted.

00:37:03.053 --> 00:37:07.199
And may we hear your calling afresh and anew.

00:37:07.239 --> 00:37:17.033
That you are a caller who has given each of us a calling to live a life worthy of the calling we have received.

00:37:17.774 --> 00:37:21.860
So Lord, may your calling and our living be congruent.

00:37:22.601 --> 00:37:26.546
And that first call for all of us is to follow Jesus.

00:37:27.234 --> 00:37:30.879
And if you're here today, I've never made that decision to follow Jesus.

00:37:31.580 --> 00:37:37.529
I want to invite you right now to just answer the calling of the Lord and say, Lord, thank you for calling me.

00:37:38.430 --> 00:37:46.201
Thank you for going to the cross and rising from the dead to save me, to rescue me, to offer me new life and forgiveness.

00:37:46.241 --> 00:37:49.085
And so I ask for your forgiveness, God.

00:37:50.387 --> 00:37:51.328
I receive it now.

00:37:52.409 --> 00:37:55.634
And I say yes to following you.

00:38:00.034 --> 00:38:00.995
Maybe that's you today.

00:38:02.398 --> 00:38:07.866
Say, Lord, yes, I choose to follow you to be your disciple.

00:38:09.489 --> 00:38:17.781
And for those of us who has made that calling, Lord, I pray today we would answer the call to be the disciple you would want us to be this day.

00:38:19.063 --> 00:38:20.786
So thank you for your grace.

00:38:20.930 --> 00:38:23.352
Thank you for your love and thank you for your calling.

00:38:23.593 --> 00:38:26.576
May we live lives worthy of this calling that we have received.

00:38:26.836 --> 00:38:34.003
For God's greater glory, for the good of the world and for our joy, we pray all these things in Jesus' name and everyone said together, amen.

00:38:38.047 --> 00:38:41.951
Thanks for listening to the Crossway Christian Church's Milford Campus Sermit Podcast.

00:38:42.251 --> 00:38:49.618
If you'd like to plug into the life of our community or have any questions that we might be able to answer, visit our website at crosswaycc.org to connect with us.

00:38:49.858 --> 00:38:51.215
Until next time, we can be with you.

00:38:51.539 --> 00:38:53.138
May the Lord bless you and keep you.
